---
title: Bacon Linguine in Blush Sauce with Baby Tomatoes, Corn and Crispy Shallots
description: Everyone loves Alfredo, and this one is blushing! The swirl of rosy colour in this luscious linguine dish comes from sweet baby tomatoes. The sauce is boosted even more with bacon and corn and a sprinkle of crispy shallots. You'll be licking the plate clean!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/linguines-au-bacon-dans-une-sauce-tomate-cremeuse-ff90f16d.jpg
